<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Cloud Systems</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      font-family: "Segoe UI", system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: #eef2f7;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* ── Header ── */
    header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #005ea2 0%, #0078d4 100%);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 1.1rem 2rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .hd-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .9rem; }
    header h1 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .04em; }

    .status-pill {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .4rem;
      font-size: .68rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .07em; text-transform: uppercase;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.25);
      border-radius: 99px;
      padding: .22rem .75rem;
    }
    .status-dot {
      width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: #57ff57;
      box-shadow: 0 0 7px #57ff57;
      animation: blink 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes blink { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:.3} }

    .hd-clocks {
      text-align: right;
      font-size: .8rem;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .1rem;
      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
      opacity: .9;
    }
    #clock-local { opacity: .65; font-size: .72rem; }

    /* ── Layout ── */
    main {
      max-width: 1040px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem 3rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1.25rem;
      align-items: start;
    }
    @media (max-width: 680px) { main { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    .right { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem; }

    /* ── Cards ── */
    .card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.06), 0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,.06);
      padding: 1.4rem 1.5rem;
    }
    .card-title {
      font-size: .68rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .1em; color: #0078d4;
      margin-bottom: .9rem;
      padding-bottom: .6rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
    }

    /* ── Infra table ── */
    .infra-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
    .infra-table tr.data { border-bottom: 1px solid #f2f2f2; }
    .infra-table tr.data:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .infra-table tr.data:hover td { background: #f4f8fd; }
    .infra-table td { padding: .55rem .3rem; font-size: .875rem; vertical-align: top; transition: background .12s; }
    .infra-table td:first-child { color: #706e6c; width: 46%; }
    .infra-table td:last-child { color: #1a1a1a; font-weight: 500; }
    .infra-table tr.section-row td {
      font-size: .65rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .1em; color: #0078d4;
      padding-top: 1.1rem; padding-bottom: .3rem;
    }
    .infra-table tr.section-row:first-child td { padding-top: .1rem; }

    /* ── Highlights ── */
    .highlights { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .75rem; }
    .highlights li {
      font-size: .855rem; color: #333; line-height: 1.55;
      padding-left: 1.15rem; position: relative;
    }
    .highlights li::before { content: "→"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #0078d4; font-weight: 700; }

    /* ── Visitor table ── */
    .vis-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
    .vis-table tr { border-bottom: 1px solid #f2f2f2; }
    .vis-table tr:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .vis-table td { padding: .5rem .3rem; font-size: .855rem; vertical-align: top; }
    .vis-table td:first-child { color: #706e6c; width: 40%; }
    .vis-table td:last-child { color: #1a1a1a; font-weight: 500; }
    .mono { font-family: "Cascadia Code", "Fira Code", "Courier New", monospace; font-size: .77rem; word-break: break-all; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="hd-left">
      <h1>Cloud Systems</h1>
      <div class="status-pill"><span class="status-dot"></span>Operational</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hd-clocks">
      <span id="clock-utc">UTC —:—:—</span>
      <span id="clock-local"></span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <!-- Left: infrastructure facts -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Infrastructure</div>
      <table class="infra-table">
        <tr class="section-row"><td colspan="2">Host</td></tr>
        <tr class="data"><td>Domain</td><td>{{ app_domain }}</td></tr>
        <tr class="data"><td>Region</td><td>Azure South Central US</td></tr>
        <tr class="data"><td>Protocol</td><td>HTTP/2, TLS 1.2/1.3</td></tr>
        <tr class="data"><td>Certificate</td><td>Let's Encrypt (auto-renewing)</td></tr>

        <tr class="section-row"><td colspan="2">Stack</td></tr>
        <tr class="data"><td>Web server</td><td>nginx</td></tr>
        <tr class="data"><td>Database</td><td>MariaDB</td></tr>
        <tr class="data"><td>Provisioning</td><td>Terraform</td></tr>
        <tr class="data"><td>Configuration</td><td>Ansible</td></tr>
        <tr class="data"><td>Secrets</td><td>Ansible Vault</td></tr>
        <tr class="data"><td>State</td><td>Azure Blob Storage</td></tr>
        <tr class="data"><td>AI interface</td><td>MCP over SSE</td></tr>

        <tr class="section-row"><td colspan="2">Network</td></tr>
        <tr class="data"><td>App subnet</td><td>10.0.1.0/24 (public)</td></tr>
        <tr class="data"><td>DB subnet</td><td>10.0.2.0/24 (private)</td></tr>
        <tr class="data"><td>DB access</td><td>App subnet only</td></tr>
        <tr class="data"><td>SSH</td><td>Via bastion only</td></tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: about + visitor -->
    <div class="right">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">About this project</div>
        <ul class="highlights">
          <li>Fully automated two-tier deployment: one <code>terraform apply</code> provisions the network, VMs, and NSGs; one <code>ansible-playbook</code> configures everything.</li>
          <li>Self-healing: Terraform writes the live public IP into Ansible's group vars on every apply, so the stack always converges to the correct state automatically.</li>
          <li>Zero-trust network segmentation: the database is unreachable from the internet; only the app subnet can connect on port 3306.</li>
          <li>Secrets stay encrypted at rest with Ansible Vault; Terraform state lives in Azure Blob Storage, never on a local machine.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">Your connection</div>
        <table class="vis-table">
          <tr><td>Browser</td><td id="v-browser"></td></tr>
          <tr><td>OS</td><td id="v-os"></td></tr>
          <tr><td>Language</td><td id="v-lang"></td></tr>
          <tr><td>Screen</td><td id="v-screen"></td></tr>
          <tr><td>CPU threads</td><td id="v-cpu"></td></tr>
          <tr><td>Cookies</td><td id="v-cookies"></td></tr>
          <tr><td>Page load</td><td id="v-load"></td></tr>
          <tr><td>User agent</td><td id="v-ua" class="mono"></td></tr>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <script src="/session.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
